Package ch.nolix.core.validator2

Class Validator

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.nolix.core.validator2.Validator

  • public final class Validator
extends java.lang.Object
    The validator provides functions to validate arguments. Methods are called on objects, functions are called independently. Of this class no instance can be created.
    Author:
    Silvan Wyss
